msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Erina told me to wait right around here."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Yo, you were pretty quick."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "I was so excited to meet up with you that\r\nI cut out a little early. <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Hey, you sure that's going to be okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "It's no prob. Come on, let's go. <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nI know exactly which restaurant I want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Alright then.\r\n...Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "Hm? What's the matter?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "...No, it was nothing.\r\nLet's get going."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Yep! <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "I can't shake the feeling that\r\nwe're being watched..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "It's so nice to be out with you, Kiryu-san.\r\nWhat should I order?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "It's on me, so get anything you want."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Are you sure?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "I'm not the type of guy to go back on my word."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "Thank you! Then I'll take you up on your offer...\r\nExcuse me!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "Um, I'll have this, an order of this and that...\r\nOne of these... An order of that, too..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "This one, this one... And an extra one of these! This on the side... \r\nand definitely the one that put them on the map!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "......!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "What a feast!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "Ahhh, everything was so delicious! <symbol=note_with_outline>\r\nThank you for the meal, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "U-Uh... You really can scarf it down..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I wasn't lying when I said I ate big...\r\nOh, that restaurant looks pretty good too..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "Y-You're still hungry?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "I don't stay full very long, I guess...\r\nKind of explains why I don't eat out, doesn't it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "You've got it bad..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "...Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san?\r\nIs something wrong?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "I figured as much. We're being followed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "What!? Followed!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Wait!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Hey, you. You've been stalking us for a while,\r\nhaven't you?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "W-Who are you to accuse me of that!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "I-I-I was just keeping an eye on you to make sure\r\nyou didn't do anything to hurt Erina-chan!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Huh? What are you talking about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Poor, sweet Erina-chan... Getting forced to\r\nhang out with this big yakuza lug..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "Ah, you're...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "You know this guy?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Of course she does! We're an item!\r\nW-W-We're in love...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "What...?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "W-We aren't an \"item,\" and we're certainly not\r\nin love!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "We only met once at a school club!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "No need to be so shy about us, Erina-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "You were so sweet to me...\r\nI know you really like me, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "N-No... You've got the wrong idea..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "Besides, how can you say we've only met once?\r\nI watch over you every day, Erina-chan."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "What? Every day?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Looks like we solved your stalker problem...\r\nThis must be our guy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "N-No way..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "Why don't you ditch this thug and come have\r\nfun with me, Erina-chan?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "K-Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "That's enough.\r\nYou're making a fool of yourself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Shut up! Who do you think are, talking to me like\r\nthat!? And how dare you act so close to Erina-chan!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "You... Just who are you to Erina-chan!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Erina is..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "...my girl."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san...!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "That's why...\r\nI'm not letting you anywhere near her."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Excuse me!?\r\nI'm Erina's real boyfriend, asshole!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Ahh!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "Anyone who gets in my way... has to die!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Agh... Son of a..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Don't ever speak another word to Erina again.\r\nIf you even come near her, you'll regret it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "E-Erina-chan..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "I can't go out with you, and there's no need for\r\nyou to watch over me, okay?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "I... already have someone special..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "D... Dammit...! You asshooooole!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "Thank you so much...\r\n...I've caused a lot of trouble for you."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Don't worry about it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "...Maybe I'm just bad at this romance thing.\r\nIt never seems to work out in my favor."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "People I'm not even pursuing get the wrong idea,\r\nand other people I like think I'm too fake..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "You've had a rough go of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "It was enough to make me want to give up\r\non romance for a while."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "But lately, I've been thinking I need to keep\r\nputting myself out there..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "Yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "But I was really surprised back there...\r\nWhen... When you called me your girl."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "Oh, sorry about that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "80||||4"
msgid "I figured if I lied to him like that,\r\nit might make him back down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "81||||4"
msgid "N-No, I was just surprised.\r\nIt actually made me happy."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "82||||4"
msgid "And then... I thought maybe it wouldn't\r\nhave to stay a lie..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "83||||4"
msgid "Hm?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "84||||4"
msgid "N-Nothing!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "85||||4"
msgid "But... considering your track record Erina,\r\nthere may be other guys who get the wrong idea, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "86||||4"
msgid "I think I've figured out that I'm being too nice,\r\nall because I want to be liked in return."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "87||||4"
msgid "But all I've accomplished by doing that is hurting\r\nother people and sabotaging my own chances..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "88||||4"
msgid "......"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "89||||4"
msgid "So from now on,\r\nI'm going to be honest with myself."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "90||||4"
msgid "Worrying about how people think of me, or whether\r\nor not they like me... I'm done being tied down by that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "91||||4"
msgid "Hm... Sounds like you've finally figured it out.\r\nDoes that mean we can say goodbye to fake Erina?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "92||||4"
msgid "Yep, from today on, no more fake Erina.\r\nI won't put on a show of being so sweet anymore."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "93||||4"
msgid "But, to balance that out...\r\nmaybe I'll be more assertive with people I like?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "94||||4"
msgid "Really?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "95||||4"
msgid "Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

